nd beat the frosting until it reaches your desired consistency. This should only take a minute or two.\n\n8. Transfer the frosting to a piping bag or use a spatula to spread it on your cake or cupcakes. If you're not using it immediately, store it in an airtight container in the fridge for up to 3 days.\n\nHelpful Tips:\n\n- Make sure the cream cheese and butter are both softened at room"
